column5: Hi Everyone,  I am looking to make my own culling tags, but was wondering if anyone knew where to buy the floats similar to the floats shown on these culling tags.  Thanks in advance
Nothing special Michaels.  Go over to big fat bass more tourney guys there.
also, where I might be able to get some of these Berkley clips?  I'm not sure they make them anymore, think they have gone to a smaller style clip now.
I have a set. Maybe JB's or Natural Sports. And BJ Tackle they will be at Bellville show this weekend.
Those are discontinued, they have small clips that are similar but they dont stay on like the big ones.
